      "writtenOn": "2020-08-06T17:48:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I\u0027m not really sure if that will always be a mistake. Just like my example above, I assume different test frameworks may have different needs on how to categorize their results. But on a second thought, if this example can be a legit case, maybe they can use test framework as the top level category and the conflict would be solved.",
